public interface LoadListener

Interface LoadListener defines one method, that will be called by a Loader, when a LoadEvent is casted.

Method Detail

imageLoaded

public void imageLoaded(LoadEvent e)
Predefines an event-reaction method. It is called by start of loading, complete loading of images of a certain level, finish of loading or a loading error.
Parameters:
e - the LoadEvent being casted.
